title: Chicago Metallic® Batter Dispenser
description:
Easily dispense the perfect amount of batter with no messy drips. Great for pancakes, waffles, cupcakes, and more. Simply fill with batter, position dispenser over pan, and pull handle for quick, precise dispensing. 
The product featured in this video can be purchased at: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-976589/Chicago-Metallic-Batter-Dispenser---
